def f_gold(s: str) -> List[str]:   # --- py stmt 1
    def dfs(i, t, lcnt, rcnt, ldel, rdel):   # --- py stmt 2
        nonlocal tdel, ans   # --- py stmt 3
        if ldel * rdel < 0 or lcnt < rcnt or ldel + rdel > len(s) - i:   # --- py stmt 4
            return   # --- py stmt 5
        if ldel == 0 and rdel == 0:   # --- py stmt 6
            if len(s) - len(t) == tdel:   # --- py stmt 7
                ans.add(t)   # --- py stmt 8
        if i == len(s):   # --- py stmt 9
            return   # --- py stmt 10
        if s[i] == '(':   # --- py stmt 11

            dfs(i + 1, t + '(', lcnt + 1, rcnt, ldel, rdel)   # --- py stmt 13
        elif s[i] == ')':   # --- py stmt 14
            dfs(i + 1, t, lcnt, rcnt, ldel, rdel - 1)   # --- py stmt 15
            dfs(i + 1, t + ')', lcnt, rcnt + 1, ldel, rdel)   # --- py stmt 16
        else:   # --- py stmt 17

    ldel = rdel = 0   # --- py stmt 19

    ans = set()   # --- py stmt 29
    dfs(0, '', 0, 0, ldel, rdel)   # --- py stmt 30
    return list(ans)   # --- py stmt 31
